title: Rooftop Ritmo
description:
🔥 Rooftop Ritmo – Latin Tech House Party 🔥

Presented by The Hibernia Bank & Dirty Not Sorry

Join us for a sun-soaked afternoon of vibrant beats and rooftop vibes at Rooftop Ritmo, a Latin tech house celebration at one of San Francisco’s most iconic venues — The Hibernia Bank!

🌴 Expect infectious rhythms, city views, and an all-star lineup bringing the heat from 3PM to 8PM:

✨ Eyezick

✨ Knives

✨ Navii

✨ Jero b2b Robert Raya

✨ Will Bonara

Let’s dance under the sky and celebrate Latin culture through house music with some of the Bay Area’s finest selectors.

📍 The Hibernia Bank – 1 Jones St, San Francisco, CA 94103

📅 Saturday, May 31st

🕒 3PM – 8PM

🎟️ Limited tickets available – secure your spot early!

This is more than a party — it’s a rooftop movement. Come feel the Ritmo. 🌞

21+ ONLY – ID REQUIRED
